  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Property Executive",
  "description": "<p>At Ohmyhome Property Managment, we are the leading company that uses information technology tool, to handle the majority of administrative tasks faced at ground. However, we believe our staff is our best Ambassador and will carry out their duties with high level of integrity and reliability.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>We are looking for <strong>Property Executive</strong>, who are able to:</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><u><strong>Job Description:</strong></u></p>\n<p>-Manage and maintain Residential property sites as assigned</p>\n<p>-Conduct Regulation Checks and inspection on ground to ensure property is well maintained</p>\n<p>-Ensure building statutory requirement are complied with</p>\n<p>-Provide essential customer service support to resident and owner</p>\n<p>-Review and recommend replacement/ improvement plan for the site</p>\n<p>-Perform other duties as assigned</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><u><strong>Job Requirement:</strong></u></p>\n<p>- Possess Diploma in Real Estate Management or equivalent</p>\n<p>- Minimum 1-3 years of experience in Real Estate Management or related field</p>\n<p>- Love to work and interact with People</p>\n<p>- Strong leadership quality and problem solver</p>\n<p>- Good communication and written skill</p>\n<p>- Able to start immediately will be advantageous</p>\n<p>- Able to prioritise tasks and passion in Building Management</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Interested candidate please click to apply with your resume indicating your current and expected salary.</p>",
